CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

December 3, 2010

[Cite as 12/03/2010 Case Announcements, 2010-Ohio-5856.]

DISCIPLINARY CASES

2009-1544. Disciplinary Counsel v. Nicks.

This cause came on for further consideration upon the filing by respondent, J. Michael Nicks, of an affidavit of compliance and a motion to cure contempt. Upon consideration thereof,

It is ordered by the court that the motion is granted.
